Package: jugglr
Title: Juggling Pattern Validation and Visualisation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ella", "Kaye", , "ella.kaye@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Validate and visualise juggling patterns expressed in siteswap
    notation. Supports vanilla, synchronous, multiplex, synchronous multiplex,
    and passing siteswap, with tools to check pattern validity, produce timeline
    arc diagrams and ladder diagrams, retrieve raw throw data for custom
    visualisations, and animate patterns via the 'JugglingLab' animation
    server (<https://jugglinglab.org/>).
